#: app/Services/TransStrings.php
msgid ""
"is a free and open-source WordPress Plugin. Our mission is to provide the "
"ultimate email delivery solution with your favorite Email sending service. "
"FluentSMTP is built for performance and speed."
msgstr ""
"是一款免費且開源的 WordPress 外掛。我們的使命是配合你喜愛的電子郵件傳送服務，"
"提供極致的電子郵件遞送解決方案。FluentSMTP 是為了效能與速度而生。"

#: app/Services/TransStrings.php
